{"word":"G4931 - συντελέω - synteléō - soon-tel-eh'-o - End","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συντελέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synteléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-tel-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">End</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முடி, நிறைவேறு, ஏற்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"1. to end together or at the same time"},{"paragraph":"2. to end completely; bring to an end, finish, complete:"},{"paragraph":"3. to accomplish, bring to fulfillment"},{"paragraph":"4. to effect, make"},{"paragraph":"5. to finish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G5055 - τελέω - teléō - tel-eh'-o/5055\">G5055</a>; to <i>complete entirely</i>; generally to <i>execute</i> (literally or figuratively): - end, finish, fulfil, make.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2005/2005\">G2005</a>, <a href=\"#/G3838/3838\">G3838</a>, <a href=\"#/G4930/4930\">G4930</a>, <a href=\"#/G4931/4931\">G4931</a>, <a href=\"#/G5046/5046\">G5046</a>, <a href=\"#/G5047/5047\">G5047</a>, <a href=\"#/G5048/5048\">G5048</a>, <a href=\"#/G5049/5049\">G5049</a>, <a href=\"#/G5050/5050\">G5050</a>, <a href=\"#/G5051/5051\">G5051</a>, <a href=\"#/G5052/5052\">G5052</a>, <a href=\"#/G5055/5055\">G5055</a>, <a href=\"#/G5056/5056\">G5056</a>"}]}